Biology and notes. This flower fly species has been recorded visiting different plant species such as
Azorella compacta Phil.
(Michael Weymann, CSP record);
Calendula officinalis
L. (Mila Val, CSP record);
Encelia canescens Lam
(Rodrigo Barahona-Segovia, pers. obs.);
E. pectinatus
(Peter Lewis, CSP record); Orizoë sp. (Daniel Llavaneras, CSP record);
Senecio
sp. (Ana María Gutiérrez, CSP record). Other aspects of its biology and ecology remain unknown in Chile .
